| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5363 — Recovery Inhibition (blackbasta)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0e498b6f-4bef-5e70-98f8-8bbc2d8e1491"
